title: pixel 3 does not support airtel wifi calling but pixel 3a supports after june security patch. Why?
content:
pixel 3 does not support airtel wifi calling but pixel 3a supports after june security patch. Why?
Airtel says google will provide support and google says airtel has to enable it. If airtel has to enable it than how come it stated working with june security patch on pixel 3a and 3a xl.
